Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:06.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "El lladre de joies Iwao Takatori estava acorralat."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:10.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Mentre, jo resolia el cas\Nfent-me passar pel Kogoro Dorment."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.92,Green,,0,0,0,,Correu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Alerta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.60,White,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Iah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:35.36,Green,,0,0,0,,No es mogui! Senyor Takatori,\Nno faci ni un pas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.88,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Eh? És en Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.96,White,,0,0,0,,-(home) Aixeca't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Ma... marrec!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.24,White,,0,0,0,,Val més que no es mogui ningú.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.96,White,,0,0,0,,O li rebentaré el cap a aquest nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.04,White,,0,0,0,,Li esclafaré\Ncom si fos un tomàquet madur.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.40,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:55.68,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.44,Green,,0,0,0,,Alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.64,White,,0,0,0,,-(Chiba) S'escapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:03.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "L'Iwao Takatori\Nno m'ha segrestat perquè sí:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:05.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"volia que l'ajudés a recuperar\Nles pedres precioses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:08.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"que s'havia emportat el seu soci,\Nun tal Tokuro Utsumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:11.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que ha traït en Takatori\Ni que ara és mort."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:16.20,White,,0,0,0,,Això és tot el que has trobat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.28,White,,0,0,0,,No et servirà de res,\Namagar les pedres.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:21.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No he amagat res, jo. De fet,\Na mi també m'ha semblat estrany.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:25.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Les pedres que han robat\Nvalen 300 milions de iens, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:28.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És evident\Nque no hi són totes, aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ha sigut ell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:35.36,White,,0,0,0,,En Tokuro es va deixar enredar\Nper la seva xerrameca.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:37.68,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que ell el va convèncer\Nperquè em matés...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.72,White,,0,0,0,,per menys de la meitat\Ndel que havíem acordat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.52,White,,0,0,0,,Que idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:44.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ell"? Qui és "ell"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir... que l'han traït?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:54.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I ara què pensa fer?\NVoldrà venjar-se d'aquesta persona?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:59.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.92,White,,0,0,0,,La teva feina ja s'ha acabat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ara procura mantenir la curiositat\Na ratlla, marrec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:13.56,White,,0,0,0,,Si et penses que no m'atreviré\Na matar-te perquè ets petit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:15.64,White,,0,0,0,,estàs molt equivocat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "On anem?\NEn quina direcció?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.40,White,,0,0,0,,(tocs de botzina)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Oh... Ha reduït la velocitat."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Per què? Què pretén fer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.28,White,,0,0,0,,Vols tornar a sortir del cotxe, noi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:50.08,White,,0,0,0,,Si estàs de sort, potser et salvaràs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:02.72,White,,0,0,0,,A reveure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "Quan el compte enrere arriba a zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,la deducció és l'única resposta."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un segrest, una xemeneia\Ni un cadàver."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:24.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Qui deu ser el traïdor misteriós?\NLa veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:32.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Honno suubyou de fukitobu mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:46.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Soshite semarareta\Nniritsu no se wo osu aa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:51.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Karamitsuita kono koodo\Nwo kiru kurai de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Konna namakura ga omotai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,furuete shimau shimatsu da.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kagen shirazu no sujigaki de
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,saishuukai temae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:09.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima byouyomi no owari ga temaneku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:15.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi no inai mirai nante\Nerabitaku mo nai yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:21.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ichibyou saki no boku\Nyo kotae wo dashite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:29.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kagen shirazu no sujigaki de
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,saishuukai temae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:38.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima byouyomi no owari ga temaneku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:43.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi no inai mirai nante\Nerabitaku mo nai yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:49.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ichibyou saki no boku\Nyo kotae wo dashite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:53.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:58.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El segrest d'en Conan\N(segona part)"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Ah..., mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "On dec ser?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"On he anat a parar?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah..., mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.16,White,,0,0,0,,(tocs de botzina)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:26.32,Green,,0,0,0,,De... de debò? Ha aparegut en Conan?\NL'heu trobat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.80,White,,0,0,0,,Què? On és, ara? Està ferit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.24,Green,,0,0,0,,O sigui que una xemeneia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Al fons de tot hi he trobat el cos\Nde l'altre lladre de joies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,el còmplice,\Naquest tal Tokuro Utsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.32,White,,0,0,0,,El devia matar l'Iwao.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No va anar així, la cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.16,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Va ser a l'inrevés.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Va ser en Tokuro, qui va intentar matar l'Iwao, però va fallar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.68,White,,0,0,0,,T'ho ha dit ell, això?\NNo crec que ens en puguem fiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja, però l'Iwao Takatori m'ha dit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que algú altre havia convençut\Nen Tokuro perquè el matés
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,a canvi\Nde menys de la meitat del botí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.76,Green,,0,0,0,,"Algú altre"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.40,White,,0,0,0,,Llavors representa\Nque hi ha un altre còmplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.68,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, és algú\Nque es mou entre bastidors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:12.80,White,,0,0,0,,Si això és veritat, aquest cas és molt més complex del que semblava.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.84,Green,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.40,Green,,0,0,0,,Takagi, busca immediatament\Nla fàbrica abandonada...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.00,Green,,0,0,0,,on hi ha la xemeneia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.08,Green,,0,0,0,,Comprova que el cadàver sigui\Nd'en Tokuro Utsumi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.68,Green,,0,0,0,,i troba alguna pista que ens porti\Nfins a l'Iwao Takatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Chiba, investiga els contactes\Ndels lladres...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.84,Green,,0,0,0,,per saber qui pot ser\Nla persona misteriosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.36,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.20,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.20,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ran, hola...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.40,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Estàs ferit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Em sap molt de greu\Nhaver-te fet patir tant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.20,White,,0,0,0,,Les ferides no són greus,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:44.40,White,,0,0,0,,però se'l quedaran un parell de dies\Nen observació per si de cas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.28,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Quin descans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.16,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No hi ha dret, pare.\NPer què no me n'havies dit res?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.28,White,,0,0,0,,Perdona, pensava avisar-te...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:54.12,White,,0,0,0,,quan ens confirmessin que estava\Nsa i estalvi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.80,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Vaja. Bé, ja estic més tranquil·la.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Quina sort que no hagis pres mal,\NConan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Ran..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Estic bé,\Nnomés una mica cansat, ara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:06.96,White,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.12,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.12,Green,,0,0,0,,Bé, nosaltres anirem passant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:16.08,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí, esclar. Aneu amb compte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:16.08,White,,0,0,0,,Et quedes tu amb ell, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:20.28,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què, Conan?\NVols que et porti alguna cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Doncs, mira, ara que ho dius,\Ntinc una mica de set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.32,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Entesos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Parlaré amb la infermera i,\Nsi em dona permís,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,aniré a comprar-te un suc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,I ara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,D'acord. I gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Estira't i descansa, que ara torno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:40.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "De debò\Nque em sap greu, Ran."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ara per ara, l'única pista\Nque tenim..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:55.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,He d'aturar l'Iwao Takatori\Ncom més aviat millor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No tinc més remei que intentar-ho."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Eh? On s'ha ficat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:12.36,White,,0,0,0,,Però... què dius?\NQue ha tornat a desaparèixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:16.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Estic molt amoïnada.\NI si torna a estar en perill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,L'has de trobar\Ni portar-lo de seguida, pare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.72,White,,0,0,0,,Recoi... Aquest nano sempre es fica\Non no el demanen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sembla que ho faci expressament.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.00,Green,,0,0,0,,Li ha passat alguna cosa,\Na en Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.88,White,,0,0,0,,S'ha esfumat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.40,White,,0,0,0,,Sisplau, torni a activar\Nel dispositiu de recerca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.60,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí, ara mateix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "L'objectiu\Nde l'Iwao Takatori...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"deu ser recuperar\Nla seva part del botí
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i venjar-se d'aquesta persona\Nque l'ha traït."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.68,White,,0,0,0,,En Tokuro es va deixar enredar\Nper la seva xerrameca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.52,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que ell el va convèncer\Nperquè em matés
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.84,White,,0,0,0,,per menys de la meitat\Ndel que havíem acordat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.36,White,,0,0,0,,Que idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No l'hi permetré."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Aturi's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) És aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Allà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mhm, mhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Està tancat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Llavors, aquí...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,és on vivia el seu còmplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.88,White,,0,0,0,,No n'hi ha cap dubte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.88,White,,0,0,0,,El cadàver que hi ha a dins\Nde la xemeneia és d'en Tokuro Utsumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.76,White,,0,0,0,,el còmplice de l'Iwao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.84,White,,0,0,0,,Però al voltant del cos\Nno hi hem trobat cap pista
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.08,White,,0,0,0,,sobre la possible ubicació\Ndel senyor Takatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.96,White,,0,0,0,,Potser en Chiba trobarà alguna cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.04,White,,0,0,0,,Està investigant l'entorn\Nd'en Tokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:23.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) Què són\Ntantes escombraries?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Mm?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:33.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No fa gaire que s'han vessat."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:49.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,A-aquest home...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,era el cap de compres\Nde la joieria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I aquests són...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:06.44,White,,0,0,0,,en Tokuro Utsumi,\Nl'Iwao Takatori i el senyor Yamaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Qui és l'home de la punta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:14.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,em sembla que ja ho tinc clar,\Ntot el que ha passat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I això?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això no és...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Avui a les quatre de la tarda..., HK".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Hong Kong"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per les quatre de la tarda...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,falta una hora i mitja!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.84,White,,0,0,0,,(passes)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.04,White,,0,0,0,,(remor metàl·lica)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.64,White,,0,0,0,,(porta corredissa)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però què...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "L'Iwao Takatori!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:57.44,White,,0,0,0,,Renoi. Què li passa, a aquest nen?\NNo aprendrà mai la lliçó?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) L'ha assassinat vostè,\Nel senyor Yamaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.28,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.36,White,,0,0,0,,L'hauria pogut matar jo, sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:09.68,White,,0,0,0,,Però... no ho he fet,\Nperquè el traïdor no era ell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Llavors, qui és la persona\Nque busca? És l'altre home, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.28,White,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Esperi's un moment! Obri la porta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hauré de...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, no les porto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:32.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Merda! I ara què faig?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.88,White,,0,0,0,,He trobat l'adreça d'en Tokuro.\NHi vaig ara mateix.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.68,White,,0,0,0,,(remor)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.56,White,,0,0,0,,Mèu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què? Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I tu d'on has sortit? Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:57.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Estic de sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:57.12,White,,0,0,0,,Mèu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Arrenqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.12,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"He de saber on és."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.56,White,,0,0,0,,Soc en Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.64,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Conan, ets tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Digues, Chiba. De debò?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.96,Green,,0,0,0,,Que has trobat el senyor Yamaga\Nmort al pis d'en Tokuro Utsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.80,White,,0,0,0,,Com? Oh, no em prenguis el pèl, Conan. Digue'm on ets, va.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.76,White,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.76,Green,,0,0,0,,A Hong Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:43.08,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, em penso que té la intenció\Nd'agafar el vol...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.56,White,,0,0,0,,que surt cap a Hong Kong\Na les quatre de la tarda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.00,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.00,Green,,0,0,0,,O sigui que agafarà un avió...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.32,White,,0,0,0,,E-espera't, Conan. No em diguis\Nque vas cap a l'aeroport...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, exacte. Afanyi's, sisplau.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Gràcies. M'ha fet un favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Totes les unitats a l'aeroport,\Nara mateix!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.20,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, senyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.40,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, senyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Ui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.16,White,,0,0,0,,-(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.96,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.32,White,,0,0,0,,(tocs de botzina)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.80,White,,0,0,0,,(tocs de botzina, continuen)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.32,White,,0,0,0,,Has venut totes les pedres precioses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.00,White,,0,0,0,,i has contractat\Nunes vacances de luxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.12,White,,0,0,0,,Però t'has descuidat... la meva part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.00,White,,0,0,0,,I també vull una propina
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.08,White,,0,0,0,,per haver-li encarregat a en Tokuro\Nque em matés!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Merda!\NNo sé si hi arribaré a temps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:59.80,White,,0,0,0,,Estàs massa espantat\Nper obrir la boca, o què?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.40,White,,0,0,0,,(policia: sirena, s'atura)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Ves-te'n a l'infern!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:15.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja ho tinc!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Endavant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ajupi's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Iah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.60,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara estem en paus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Abans ha dit que em mataria encara\Nque fos petit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però en comptes de matar-me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,només m'ha deixat caure\Na la mitjana de l'autopista.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ho ha fet expressament, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Fins i tot ha reduït la velocitat,\Nho he notat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.68,White,,0,0,0,,Es pot saber... qui ets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:17.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,En Conan Edogawa. Un detectiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.16,White,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.76,White,,0,0,0,,Reconec que ets espavilat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:27.24,Green,,0,0,0,,Senyor Takatori,\Nja no té escapatòria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.96,Green,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.96,White,,0,0,0,,(Mouri) Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.24,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) El còmplice del robatori\Nde les pedres precioses
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:36.32,White,,0,0,0,,i, alhora, sospitós d'un assassinat\Ni un intent d'assassinat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:40.80,White,,0,0,0,,és a dir, el cervell de tot plegat,\Nés el propietari de la joieria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.56,White,,0,0,0,,Detingui en Teruaki Shimazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Eh? Què dius, ara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.04,Green,,0,0,0,,T'hauràs d'explicar més bé, Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:55.52,Green,,0,0,0,,¿No era l'Iwao Takatori, qui havia mort en Tokuro, el seu còmplice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.72,Green,,0,0,0,,i el cap de vendes, que\Nhavia col·laborat amb els lladres?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.92,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.76,White,,0,0,0,,En Tokuro va morir accidentalment\Nal caure per la xemeneia
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.88,White,,0,0,0,,mentre intentava matar\Nl'Iwao Takatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.96,White,,0,0,0,,I l'home que ha mort\Nel senyor Yamaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.76,White,,0,0,0,,no ha sigut cap altre\Nque en Teruaki Shimazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.88,White,,0,0,0,,Quina ximpleria!\NNo té cap prova que ho demostri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:22.64,White,,0,0,0,,Aquest home ha estat a punt\Nde matar-me, només m'he defensat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.52,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Que curiós...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Fa olor de fideus instantanis,\Nsenyor Shimazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:31.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,En deu haver menjat en algun lloc,\Noi? O potser...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.12,White,,0,0,0,,Ja me'n recordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.96,White,,0,0,0,,Al pis d'en Tokuro hi havia un pot\Nde fideus que s'havia vessat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.08,White,,0,0,0,,i algú els havia trepitjat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.12,White,,0,0,0,,Els mitjons de la víctima,\Nel senyor Yamaga, eren nets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Exacte."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:49.08,White,,0,0,0,,Per tant, el culpable ha de ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.96,Green,,0,0,0,,Senyor Shimazu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.40,Green,,0,0,0,,¿es podria treure les sabates perquè\Nli puguem examinar els mitjons,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.48,Green,,0,0,0,,si és tan amable?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:57.56,White,,0,0,0,,Però que no ho veuen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.36,White,,0,0,0,,Quina necessitat en tenia, jo,\Nd'atracar la meva pròpia joieria?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.36,White,,0,0,0,,És evident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.44,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) Ho ha fet\Nper cobrar l'assegurança
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.16,White,,0,0,0,,d'aquelles pedres precioses\Ntan cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.24,White,,0,0,0,,La investigació aviat revelarà
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.04,White,,0,0,0,,que la joieria passava\Nper una situació econòmica
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.12,White,,0,0,0,,que requeria mesures dràstiques.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.20,White,,0,0,0,,El senyor Yamaga no era\Nel seu còmplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.48,White,,0,0,0,,Vostè li va ordenar\Nque participés en el pla
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.00,White,,0,0,0,,i no va tenir més remei que acceptar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.08,White,,0,0,0,,Evidentment, no sabia\Nque seria falsament acusat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.16,White,,0,0,0,,d'haver filtrat informació\Nals lladres
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.40,White,,0,0,0,,ni que moriria assassinat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.48,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo que el va convèncer dient-li...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:36.84,White,,0,0,0,,que se'n podria anar de vacances\Na Hong Kong amb vostè i en Tokuro
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.92,White,,0,0,0,,tan bon punt s'hagués acabat tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.92,White,,0,0,0,,(homes) Salut!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:12.04,Green,,0,0,0,,S'ha de dir\Nque ets molt observador, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,He-he!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això dels fideus m'ha recordat molt la crep d'una altra persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.44,Green,,0,0,0,,Com?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.44,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ho sé perquè m'ho ha explicat\Nel senyor Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Estava a punt d'aclarir-ho tot\Ntot en aquell magatzem
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,abans que l'interrompessin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:30.40,White,,0,0,0,,(Pensa) "Mm? És...\Nel Kogoro Dorment."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.00,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) I encara hi ha\Nuna altra cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.12,White,,0,0,0,,Tot i que van fer servir màscares,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.80,White,,0,0,0,,les càmeres de seguretat van gravar\Nuna prova irrefutable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.44,White,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.96,White,,0,0,0,,(gent: crida)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:51.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ara sí que ho entenc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.84,Green,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.88,White,,0,0,0,,Darrere d'un gran detectiu\Nsempre hi ha un gran ajudant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Bé, la veritat\Nés que seria al revés..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.52,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.52,Green,,0,0,0,,L'enhorabona, Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.08,Green,,0,0,0,,Has pogut acabar l'explicació\Nque havies deixat a mitges.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.80,Green,,0,0,0,,Per fi has recuperat\Nla teva bona reputació.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Això sí que és...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,...perillós!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,("First place", Sadame)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:33.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sadamerareta you ni\Nsuki ni natte yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:38.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,anata no egao sukoshi chiisana te.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:44.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kinou yori mo kyou\Nkyou yori mo ashita
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:49.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,bokura wa kitto shiawase ni nareru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:55.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Omoi ukabete goran\Ntooi mirai no futari,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:21:03.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,shiwakucha ni natta te to te\Ntsunagi nagara sanpo shiteru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:09.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Egao wo kasanete kita hibi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:14.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,anata ga unmei no hito desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:20.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Haru natsu aki fuyu yumemite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:26.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,futari de zutto zutto ikite ikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:31.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Daiji na bokunari no yume desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:39.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Anata wo shiawase ni sasete ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.80,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Oh, quin mal de cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.72,White,,0,0,0,,Aquesta vegada m'ha fet\Nmés mal que de costum,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.80,White,,0,0,0,,això de quedar-me adormit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:52.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah... Deu ser la ressaca...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.44,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs, ara que ho dius,\Nahir vaig beure més del compte.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:57.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "No crec\Nque sigui d'ahir..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:21:59.84,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres, ja me'n descuidava.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.52,White,,0,0,0,,Té.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Moltes gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:08.76,White,,0,0,0,,Val més que truquis a la Ran.\NDeu estar preocupada per tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, esclar. Ara li truco.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, hola, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.80,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil: to de trucada)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.32,Cyan,,0,0,0,,"Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:23.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,"Es pot saber on eres, fins ara,\Ni què carai has fet?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:26.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,"Fes el favor de tornar a casa,\Nque hem de parlar molt seriosament!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:28.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:34.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Ran, t'asseguro\Nque em sap molt de greu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.80,White,,0,0,0,,Mm? Ehem, ehem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:42.00,White,,0,0,0,,Ui, perdona. No et volia espantar.\NEra com aquest, el braç?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:45.04,White,,0,0,0,,Sí que tenen un jardinet igual\Nque el nostre al terrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:47.52,White,,0,0,0,,Si el que he vist és el terrat\Nd'aquest edifici,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:49.60,White,,0,0,0,,potser aquí\Nés on han enterrat el cadàver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:51.48,White,,0,0,0,,Com s'ha desfet del cadàver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.80,White,,0,0,0,,Només hi ha una resposta:\Nno ha pogut.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:58.40,White,,0,0,0,,L'única conclusió... és que el cos\Nencara és a l'edifici, ben amagat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:00.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) "No us perdeu\Nel pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,'La detectiva adolescent\NSonoko Suzuki'."
